</svg></div></div><div class="uui-space-small"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall"><strong>Automated operations</strong></h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-large">Automated deployment and updates of infrastructure, reducing the need for manual interventions and maintaining the desired state by reconciling any differences between the desired configuration in Git and the actual infrastructure.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><article class="uui-section_layout21"><div class="uui-page-padding"><div class="uui-container-large"><div class="pt-5 pb-6"><div class="w-layout-grid uui-layout20_component-copy"><div class="uui-layout21_content-left"></div><div class="uui-layout21_content-right"><div class="uui-text-size-large mb-2">Designed to provide an iterative, holistic approach,<strong>CloudGeometry Infrastructure Management </strong>solution gives you<strong> </strong>organized and version-controlled changes anchored in a single source of truth -- fostering collaboration within your team, enhancing control, and minimizing risks.</div></div></div></div></div></div></article></section><section class="uui-section_layout21 mt-6 mb-5"><div class="uui-page-padding"><div class="uui-container-large"><div class="has-separator-bottom pb-4"><div class="w-layout-grid uui-layout20_component-copy"><div class="uui-layout21_content-left"><h2 class="uui-heading-medium">Our tool stack — powering your operational excellence</h2></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="uui-section_layout91 mb-6"><div class="uui-page-padding"><div class="uui-container-large"><div class="has-separator-bottom pb-6"><div class="uui-layout91_component"><div class="uui-text-align-center"><div class="uui-max-width-large"><div class="uui-button-row button-row-center"><div class="uui-badge is-primary"><div>Reference implementation</div></div></div><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h2 class="uui-heading-small">Boosting efficiency and innovation</h2><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">Our preferred selection of open-source tools, designed to promote efficiency &amp; foster innovation, include:</div></div></div><div class="w-layout-grid uui-layout75_list"><div class="uui-layout75_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64a33cab05d6609ad9f2dce2_cloudgeometry-aws-cncf-github.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">GitHub</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">GitHub is a globally recognized software development platform that aids collaboration, while GitHub Actions automates your software workflows, providing continuous integration and delivery.</div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64a22d04410d9ffc9633a6af_argo.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">ArgoCD</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">A GitOps continuous delivery tool for Kubernetes, ArgoCD applies changes to your environments automatically and securely based on Git commits.</div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64a22d090a2512f14c077ca3_harbor.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Harbor</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">An open-source container image registry. Harbor provides role-based access control for security, scans images for vulnerabilities, and signs images.</div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/645a369d8cfb32b26eb70f1e_helm.svg.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Helm</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">The package manager for Kubernetes, Helm helps you manage Kubernetes applications with Helm Charts that define, install, and upgrade complex Kubernetes applications.</div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/645a369ab16ec524998a7ceb_kubernetes-icon-color.svg.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Kubernetes</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">An open-source system for automating deployment, scaling, and management of containerized applications. It groups containers into logical units for easy management and discovery.</div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64ca692ce2148bffbf73dbc7_cloudgeometry-integration-trivy-aws-cncf.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Trivy</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">A simple and comprehensive vulnerability scanner for containers and other artifacts, designed to be easy to use, with high accuracy and low false-positive rates.</div></div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item is-primary-light"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/6465acb9df60830cc7fb53d0_cloudgeometry-logo__stacked.svg.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout75_icon is-large"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-large">To enhance the integration of all of these diverse tools, we’ve built <a href="https://github.com/CloudGeometry/cgdevx-core?utm_source=Infrastructure%20Management%20Hero%20Section&amp;utm_medium=main%20website&amp;utm_campaign=CGDEVX%20Core" class="link-8">CGDevX</a>, which extends their capabilities to provide a cohesive and streamlined GitOps and infrastructure management experience. <a href="https://www.cloudgeometry.io/solutions/platform-engineering" class="link-9">Learn more.</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="uui-section_layout75 mb-6"><div class="uui-page-padding"><div class="uui-container-large"><div class="has-separator-bottom"><div class="uui-layout75_component"><div class="uui-text-align-center"><div><div class="uui-button-row button-row-center"><div class="uui-badge is-primary"><div>Additional options</div></div></div><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h2 class="uui-heading-small">Expanding your choices</h2><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">We offer a range of alternative options to accommodate customers who have different system preferences or are already using certain tools.</div></div><div class="w-layout-grid uui-layout75_list"><div class="uui-layout91_item"><div class="icons__wrapper"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c1218082cf9a4e32d27ec6_cloudgeometry-cncf-gitlab-pipelines-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="icons__wrapper--ico"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c055aa1079283f424136a9_cloudgeometry-cncf-bitbucket-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" id="w-node-_3d2c9e74-dd3f-ca62-fad9-cd196aa1ce4e-36c666af" alt="" class="icons__wrapper--ico"></div><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">GitLab<br>Bitbucket<br></h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">Comparable to GitHub, they offer code hosting services with built-in CI/CD solutions.</div></div><div class="uui-layout91_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c055abd38288bedfb97a4c_anchore_logo-freelogovectors.net_.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon has-width-auto"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Anchore</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">Provides a detailed analysis of the container images in your build pipeline, promoting compliance and risk mitigation.</div></div><div class="uui-layout91_item"><div class="icons__wrapper"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c055aa06e779f715b6ee0a_cloudgeometry-cncf-jenkins-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="icons__wrapper--ico"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c055abf8f861fc810431b8_cloudgeometry-cncf-flux-cd-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" id="w-node-_34dde49a-0a41-805f-3d62-53fb11da28bc-36c666af" alt="" class="icons__wrapper--ico"></div><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Jenkins &amp; FluxCD</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">A robust combination that provides continuous integration, delivery, and deployment pipeline management, perfectly complementing your GitOps or Infrastructure-as-Code (IaC) approach.</div></div><div class="uui-layout91_item"><div class="icons__wrapper is-4"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64cae97ad4b4009bea47e429_Synk-Logo-CloudGeometry.png" loading="lazy" width="43" id="w-node-_17bc9281-5641-7a6c-3459-afacd735a0fe-36c666af" alt="Integration icon" class="icons__wrapper--ico h-small no-max-h"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c123d3a5eb283bf8e94241_cloudgeometry-cncf-snort-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" id="w-node-_17bc9281-5641-7a6c-3459-afacd735a0ff-36c666af" alt="" class="icons__wrapper--ico no-min-h"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c123d22ea4fb62e1f90fde_cloudgeometry-cncf-vault-hashicorp-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" id="w-node-c2fdb9ea-db6d-f28d-25d0-d6f0c7f35c2f-36c666af" alt="" class="icons__wrapper--ico"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c123d37f78b88b6bd8f66e_cloudgeometry-cncf-threatmapper-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" id="w-node-ddaddb2d-f589-b62c-d827-a6c65f488626-36c666af" alt="" class="icons__wrapper--ico no-min-h"></div><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Snyk, Snort, Vault, ThreatMapper</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">A comprehensive suite of security-focused tools, providing capabilities from vulnerability detection and traffic analysis, to secret management and network security scanning.</div></div><div class="uui-layout91_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c055aafac265b196a55f5d_cloudgeometry-cncf-nexus-repository-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">Nexus Repository</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">A repository manager that allows you to proxy, collect, and manage your dependencies so that you are not constantly juggling a collection of JARs.</div></div><div class="uui-layout91_item"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c11e6f397f6590fd1e07b3_cloudgeometry-cncf-keda-kcsp.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout91_icon"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h3 class="uui-heading-xxsmall">KEDA</h3><div class="uui-space-xxsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-medium">A Kubernetes-based event-driven autoscaling component that enables any container to scale from zero to potentially thousands of instances based on event metrics.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="uui-section_layout91 section__odd"><div class="uui-page-padding"><div class="uui-container-large"><div class="has-separator-bottom pb-6"><div class="uui-layout91_component"><div class="uui-text-align-center"><div class="uui-max-width-large"><div class="uui-button-row button-row-center"><div class="uui-badge is-primary"><div>Commercial partnership</div></div></div><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><h2 class="uui-heading-small">JFrog — Revolutionizing DevOps together</h2><div class="uui-space-medium"></div></div></div><div class="uui-layout75_item bg-white"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6454b092740d867bde0c25eb/64c0694a4aa4f4832e92c605_cloudgeometry-jfrog-partner.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Integration icon" class="uui-layout75_icon has-no-dimensions"><div class="uui-space-xsmall"></div><div class="uui-text-size-large">CloudGeometry serves as strategic partner delivering consulting &amp; integration services for <a href="https://jfrog.com/partner/cloudgeometry/" target="_blank"><strong class="bold-text-5">JFrog</strong></a>, the global platform leader in continuous software supply chain for DevOps &amp; Security. Whether you're already using JFrog solutions or prefer commercial products over open-source tools, as certified JFrog consultants, we can flawlessly integrate and optimize JFrog's robust offerings into your DevOps pipeline.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="uui-section_layout21 my-6"><div class="uui-page-padding"><div class="uui-container-large"><div><div class="w-layout-grid uui-layout20_component-copy"><div class="uui-layout21_content-left"><h2 class="uui-heading-medium">Choose Us — Experience the edge</h2></div><div class="uui-layout21_content-right"><div class="uui-text-size-large mb-2">Looking to level up your infrastructure management and GitOps? We've got the knowledge, tools, and an in-house reference implementation, <strong class="bold-text-4">CGDevX</strong>, that will make a real difference in your workflow. Let's work together to refine your infrastructure management processes.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="uui-section_cta05"><div class="bg__decor page-padding"><div class="container-large"><div class="